Class Token_Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.uima.jcas.cas.TOP_Type

  • public class Token_Type
extends org.apache.uima.jcas.tcas.Annotation_Type
    Annotation on a token, which may have arguments if they are predicates; useful in transforming text into a "logical form", with affordances similar to the ones provided in Extended WordNet and the like. --- Source: Murdock Updated by JCasGen Sat Nov 29 22:03:38 EST 2014
